\s1 Pablo me³-le⁴ nca³ coai⁴ ya⁴ Roma
\p 
\v 22 Coi³ cjoa⁴-vi⁴ nca³ ncjin² cˀa³ qui³sˀe³chjoa²-na³ nca³ cjoa²ˀai⁴con³-no³ nca³ jon² tsa²cai³.
